Source: R/03-recode_anthro.R
recode_height.Rd

Function to recode height variable

recode_height(df)

Arguments

df

A data.frame collected for the Myanmar MCCT Programme Evaluation Study containing anthropometric data

Value

A vector of recoded heights based on any re-testing done
